                            <h2 class="title_h2">Nationwide Legal & Document Services</h2>
            
                <div class="service_content service_content_2">
                    <div class="service_intro ">
                                                    <div class="wrap_text">
                                <div class="text-content">
                                    <p>A leader in the legal services industry, One Source Process is a full service process serving and document processing company that provides an experienced, efficient, and personal service to our clients. Strategically headquartered in Washington, DC, with satellite locations nationwide, we serve all 50 states and territories, providing a variety of services such as service of process, document apostille &amp; legalization, skip-tracing, traveling notary, court filing, document retrieval, and subpoena preparation.</p>
<p>With our vast local and national network, our various legal services treat each case with the utmost priority, assuring that the job is done quickly and correctly the first time.</p>
                                </div>
                            
