     <section class="document__processing">
        <div class="container">
            <div class="document-card-wrapper">
                                                                                                    
                        <div class="document-card">
                            <div class="document-card__map">
                                                                <img src="https://www.onesourceprocess.com/wp-content/uploads/2025/01/Professional-Process-Servers_2.png" alt="Nationwide Legal & Document Services">
                                                            </div>
                            <div class="document-card__intro">
                                                                    <h2 class="title_h2">Legal Process Services</h2>
                                
                                                                    <p><p>One Source Process is the process service company that provides the most comprehensive, professional, and efficient legal document processing services in DC and all 50 states &amp; territories. The professionals who work for our DC office are trained to handle common situations that arise when serving process in the DMV, such as the difficult process of gaining access to secured residential buildings or the proper contact when serving various government agencies.</p>
<p>Need a service after hours, on the weekend, or a holiday? Our emergency answering system and after-hours availability will have your service request handled by a Washington, DC process server the same day. Upon completion of service we will file the affidavit at any DC court free of charge.</p>
</p>
                                                                    
                                                    </div>
                    </div>
                                                                
                        <div class="document-card document-card--reverse">
                            <div class="document-card__map">
                                                                <img src="https://www.onesourceprocess.com/wp-content/uploads/2025/01/Frame-28-1.png" alt="Nationwide Legal & Document Services">
                                                            </div>
                            <div class="document-card__intro">
                                                                    <h2 class="title_h2">Our Process Serving Technology</h2>
                                
                                                                    <p><p>Our proprietary process serving software provides an easy solution for our process servers to record and track their caseload. Compliance features assure clients attempts are made in a timely manner by recording each attempt with photo and GPS information. No more waiting for updates or affidavits. Everything is streamlined for your firm&#8217;s ease of use. Email us today at info@onesourceprocess.com to inquire about a demo of our services.</p>
</p>
                                                                    
                                                    </div>
                    </div>
                                                </div>
                            <div class="wrap_btn" style="margin-top: 40px;">
                                            <a class="btn" href="/send-us-a-job/"
                        target="_self">Order now</a>
                                    </div>
                    </div>
    </section>

    <section class="faq">
        <div class="container">
                            <h2 class="title_h2">Questions about service</h2>
            
            <div class="row">
                <div class="col-xl-12 col-lg-12 col-md-12 col-12">
                                    </div>
                <div class="col-xl-6 col-lg-6 col-md-12 col-12">
                                            <div class="accordion">
                            <div class="accordion__item">
                                <div class="accordion__title">
                                    <h3 class="accordion__title-text">Who is One Source Process?</h3>
                                    <div class="accordion__arrow">
                                        <img src="https://www.onesourceprocess.com/wp-content/themes/one-source-process/assets/img/minus.svg" alt="" class="minus">
                                        <img src="https://www.onesourceprocess.com/wp-content/themes/one-source-process/assets/img/minus.svg" alt="" class="plus">
                                    </div>
                                </div>
                                <div class="accordion__content" style="display: none;">
                                    One Source Process is a document processing company that provides an experienced, efficient, and personal service to our clients. <br>
Strategically headquartered in Washington, DC, with locations nationwide, we serve all 50 states and territories, providing a variety of services such as service of process, apostille & legalization, skip tracing, traveling notary, court filing, document retrieval and subpoena preparation.<br>

With our vast local and national network, our service of process company is able to treat each case with the utmost priority, assuring that the job is done quickly and correctly the first time.                                </div>
                            </div>
                        </div>

                                            <div class="accordion">
                            <div class="accordion__item">
                                <div class="accordion__title">
                                    <h3 class="accordion__title-text">How does skip-tracing work?</h3>
                                    <div class="accordion__arrow">
                                        <img src="https://www.onesourceprocess.com/wp-content/themes/one-source-process/assets/img/minus.svg" alt="" class="minus">
                                        <img src="https://www.onesourceprocess.com/wp-content/themes/one-source-process/assets/img/minus.svg" alt="" class="plus">
                                    </div>
                                </div>
                                <div class="accordion__content" style="display: none;">
                                    Our skip-tracing services involve using a variety of information resources to locate people who don’t want to be found, or to find people who have a stake or a role in a legal proceeding such as a lawsuit or an estate settlement. <br>
Clients such as attorneys, process servers, bail bondsmen and others use skip tracing to find current addresses, telephone numbers, identification numbers, workplaces and more.                                </div>
                            </div>
                        </div>

                                            <div class="accordion">
                            <div class="accordion__item">
                                <div class="accordion__title">
                                    <h3 class="accordion__title-text">Do I need a process server?</h3>
                                    <div class="accordion__arrow">
                                        <img src="https://www.onesourceprocess.com/wp-content/themes/one-source-process/assets/img/minus.svg" alt="" class="minus">
                                        <img src="https://www.onesourceprocess.com/wp-content/themes/one-source-process/assets/img/minus.svg" alt="" class="plus">
                                    </div>
                                </div>
                                <div class="accordion__content" style="display: none;">
                                    If you’re involved in legal action against another individual or organization, a process server ensures that the other party have been served with the necessary documents. Hiring a legal process server may be necessary depending on the laws in your state.<br>

One Source Process provides professional process service for several applications and situations nationwide. We are the best source online for process servers because our people have the experience necessary to fulfill even the most challenging situations. For example, we can track down individuals who may be avoiding service. In many cases, we can provide service within the first 24 hours of contacting us. Read on to learn more about everything we can do for you.                                </div>
                            </div>
                        </div>

                                            <div class="accordion">
                            <div class="accordion__item">
                                <div class="accordion__title">
                                    <h3 class="accordion__title-text">How do I submit a request?</h3>
                                    <div class="accordion__arrow">
                                        <img src="https://www.onesourceprocess.com/wp-content/themes/one-source-process/assets/img/minus.svg" alt="" class="minus">
                                        <img src="https://www.onesourceprocess.com/wp-content/themes/one-source-process/assets/img/minus.svg" alt="" class="plus">
                                    </div>
                                </div>
                                <div class="accordion__content" style="display: none;">
                                    Our specialists are standing by Monday through Friday, between the hours of 9am and 6pm eastern time to process your requests and answer any questions you may have. <br>
You can begin by sending us your requirements through our Order Form. Your assigned specialist will email you a quote once paid, your server will begin their attempts!                                </div>
                            </div>
                        </div>

                                    </div>
                <div class="col-xl-6 col-lg-6 col-md-12 col-12">
                                    </div>
            </div>
        </div>
    </section>
    <section class="section_from">
        <div class="container">
            <div class="row">
                <div class="col-xl-6 col-lg-6 col-md-12 col-12">
